Precious metals miner Sibanye-Stillwater has received formal notification that the Public Investment Corporation (PIC) has increased its total shareholding in Sibanye from 14.39% to 15.155%. Sibanye is a multinational precious metals mining company, with a portfolio of platinum group metalsÂ projects in South Africa and the US, as well as gold and base metals operations and various mining projects in South Africa and the Americas.